cast.overview: A young boy wins a tour through the most magnificent chocolate factory in the world, led by the world's most unusual candy maker.
cast.title: Charlie and the Chocolate Factory

details.biography: Janine Bellis was a model who did photography work for Contessa in 1992 as well as working for Chris Evans Photography on many corporate projects. In 1993 she became a singer/songwriter and took the stage name of Jynine James. She has appeared on TV presenting awards, giving interviews and performing tracks from her various albums. She is a stage actress as well as a singer appearing in various productions from 1992-present.
details.name: Jynine James
